      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-5">
        <BrutalCard color="#ffffff" class="p-5 border-2 border-black shadow-[6px_6px_0_0_#000] rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">P1: Role-Based Access</h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
            <li>**Ok:** Add a "Secondary Contact" to a booking.</li>
            <li>**Good:** Create "Household Profiles" with roles (Owner, Tenant) and permissions.</li>
            <li>**Moonshot:** A "Family Workspace" with shared calendars and role-based consent flows.</li>
          </ul>
        </BrutalCard>
        <BrutalCard color="#ffffff" class="p-5 border-2 border-black shadow-[6px_6px_0_0_#000] rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">P2: Unified Timeline</h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
            <li>**Ok:** Add "Internal notes for household" to a booking.</li>
            <li>**Good:** A "Unified Service Timeline" visible to all stakeholders.</li>
            <li>**Moonshot:** A "Service Feed" for each property, like a Slack channel for your home.</li>
          </ul>
        </BrutalCard>
        <BrutalCard color="#ffffff" class="p-5 border-2 border-black shadow-[6px_6px_0_0_#000] rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">P3: Live Transparency</h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
            <li>**Ok:** Mandate before/after photos from the partner.</li>
            <li>**Good:** A "Live Status" view for the remote owner (En route ‚Üí On-site ‚Üí Done).</li>
            <li>**Moonshot:** A "Remote Approval Flow" for extra costs, handled entirely in-app by the owner.</li>
          </ul>
        </BrutalCard>
