        <ul class="space-y-3 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-900">
          <li>**Adoption:** % of bookings by remote owners where an on-site contact is added. This shows the feature is being used.</li>
          <li>**Coordination Efficiency:** % reduction in "customer not available/cancelled" cases for remote-managed bookings. This shows the feature solves the coordination problem.</li>
          <li>**Retention:** % of remote-owner flagged properties that rebook within 90 days. This is the ultimate measure of value.</li>
        </ul>
