        <ol class="space-y-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-900 list-decimal list-inside">
          <li>**Identify Segment:** Target users with Indian addresses but foreign phone numbers, or those managing multiple addresses.</li>
          <li>**In-App Nudge:** On the booking screen, add a subtle prompt: "Add on-site contact (family/tenant) so they also get updates."</li>
          <li>**Lifecycle Comms:** Send an email/push to the target segment with the message: "No more coordinating 3 people on WhatsApp ‚Äì manage everything from one shared view."</li>
          <li>**Measure & Iterate:** A/B test the new flow against a control group to prove value before a broader rollout.</li>
        </ol>
